title: sap.fe.macros.richtexteditor.Plugin
content:
# sap.fe.macros.richtexteditor.Plugin

Represents a TinyMCE plugin. Each object has to contain a property "name" which then contains the plugin name/ID.

**Type:** class **Module:** sap/fe/macros/richtexteditor/Plugin
